*[_type == 'project' && !(_id in path("drafts.**")) && display != false]
{
  _id,
  _updatedAt,
  created,
  description,
  featured,
  githuburl,
  liveurl,
  techstack,
  title,
  "image": image.asset->url,
  display
} | order(featured desc)
